FashionKart ğŸ›’

FashionKart is a full-stack e-commerce platform built using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Vanilla JavaScript (Frontend).
It provides users with an interface to browse products, add items to cart, and simulate basic e-commerce functionality.

ğŸš€ Features

User-friendly UI for browsing products.

Backend API with Express and MongoDB.

RESTful routes for handling requests.

Secure connection to MongoDB Atlas.

Deployed on Render for both frontend and backend.

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Backend: Node.js, Express

Database: MongoDB Atlas

Deployment: Render

